| Depth (Z)      | 10m              |
| Height (Y)     | 10m              |
| Footprint area | 100 m²           |
| Origin         | Centred at 0,0,0 |
| Base           | Y = 0            |

Available in two formats:
- `test_cube.obj` — Wavefront OBJ, ready for Three.js direct import
- `test_cube.dxf` — DXF R2010, layers: `BUILDING_FOOTPRINT` + `BUILDING_MASS`

